      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kaẽ ta tahda irr? kas\nisrangahs ka tas Auselis? skai-\nsta ka tas Mehnes/ skaĩdra ka ta\nSaule/ bresfmiga ka (tee Kar-\nka-Spehki) ar Karregeem?"
